data.description: Renovated Antique with Granite kitchen, hardwood floors, two car garage, big backyard in the center of Rockland. It still has all of its charm and is ready for the modern family. Lots of fireplaces, interior shutters, two staircases to the second floor and a good-sized basement. Financing fell through. Please bring qualified buyers!
